e>   Chardok Raid Saturday 1/19/02</span><hr size=1> Will be running a guild raid in Chardok, starting at 2pm AST/5pm CST/6pm EST. Friends are invited as well. Need minimum 1 very good high level group. Hope to get 2 or even possibly 3 groups. Most of my raid leading experience has been limited to pickup raids in fear, and I am not extremely familiar with Chardok yet. Part of the idea for this raid is to explore Chardok more, but at least one person with a decent working knowledge of Chardok would be handy.<br><br>GOALS:<br>1. Obtain as many copies of 55 SK spell that drops here as reasonable for SK attendance, spawn time, drop rate and other mobs.<br>2. XP.<br>3. Practicing raid/multi-group tactics together.<br>4. Exploring Chardok.<br><br>ROLES:<br>Raid Leader - Geddak<br>(Will be making groups based on them being well-rounded, and equal enough to keep xp as evenly divided as possible).<br>Raid Loot - Asherea<br>(Asherea will be handling all raid loot, including getting no-drop items randomed in a timely fashion and keeping track of items dropped and items won and by whom).<br>Raid Port Whore/s - Ayepoor,Meon<br>(Will pickup at any druid ring a 39 druid can port to, and bring to dl druid ring).<br><br>NOTE:<br>This is generally how we do spell loot, but to specify for the spell that is one of the goals:<br>1. Spell will be first randomed among those of sufficient level to scribe it who do not yet have it, until all that can scribe it have. This covers everyone in the raid regardless of guild affiliation or actual level as long as they can scribe it on the spot.<br>2. Next random will be those of appropriate class to cast it, again regardless of guild or level, until they each have a copy.<br>3. As this is a guild raid, additional copies will go to the guild bank.<br><br>I will be bringing peridots from the guild bank, and putting any cash obtained from the raid back into the guild bank.<br><br>Please let me know if you can attend, and with which character. Also post if there is any specific item that you would like to be eligible to receive if it drops (don't go too overboard here, partly because I don't know which all parts of Chardok we will be exploring, but let me know if there is something that you can think of that your character attending can use).<br><br>Geddak  <p></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub49.ezboard.com/uhellefire.showPublicProfile?language=EN>hellefire</A> at: 1/16/02 12:44:29 pm<br></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#242422><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub49.ezboard.com/uvrrossbloodscale.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Vrross Bloodscale</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Tankasaurus</span><br>  Posts: 33<br> <font color=#939393>(1/10/02 1:31:14 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Chardok Raid Saturday 1/19/02</span><hr size=1> I wanna go.  I might even be of sufficient level to be useful by then. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub49.ezboard.com/ukralthan.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Kralthan</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 1<br> <font color=#939393>(1/10/02 6:16:38 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Killin stuff ... Fun !</span><hr size=1> Hey guys, count me in.  I always enjoy hunting with USV, but ... umm... do I have to be HT bait again ?  LoL<br><br><br>Kralthan<br>-edit- Guess I should add the class/lvl/guild info as requested ...<br>55 SK, UoN (Unification of Norrath) <p></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub49.ezboard.com/ukralthan.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Kralthan</A> at: 1/10/02 6:33:25 pm<br></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#242422><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub49.ezboard.com/uhellefire.showPublicProfile?language=EN>hellefi